287
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:37,360
In this scenario,

288
00:09:37,360 --> 00:09:38,440
So, for a computer,

289
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,400
As we've mentioned before,

290
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:42,320
it can then process all these texts without any discrimination.

